            <p><add hand="#barker">Introducing Stephen F. Austin.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            


<p><placeName>Herculanium </placeName><date when="1817-12-09">9th Decr. 1817</date></p>
<p>Dear Sirs</p>

<p>It gives Me particular pleasure to make you acquainted with <persName>Mr
Stephen Austin</persName>, a gentleman whose company you will be pleas'd
with and who has been of considerable service to me in this 
Country&#8212;<persName>Mr A</persName> and his <persName>Father </persName>are extensively engagd in the Mining
business, and I doubt not but your acquaintance will prove 
advantageous to each other&#8212; As My <persName>friend </persName>is an entire <persName>stranger </persName>in your
<placeName>City</placeName>, I shall esteem it a particular favour if you will give him every
information in your power; your usual civilities I think it needless
to ask as they are so universally bestow'd&#8212;in hopes of seeing you
soon believe Me</p>

<p><persName>James Cox Junr</persName>    [Rubric]</p>

<p>Messrs<persName> Macdonald</persName> and <persName>Eidgely   </persName><persName>Merchants   </persName><placeName>Baltimore</placeName></p>

        </div1>
